      <title>德意志银行聘请瑞银的 Gasser 负责德国财富管理部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/deutsche-bank-taps-ubs-s-gasser-to-run-german-wealth-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行聘请拉斐尔·加塞尔 (Raffael Gasser) 担任德国财富管理和私人银行业务主管，并任命私人银行业务主管的另一位前同事克劳迪奥·德桑克蒂斯 (Claudio de Sanctis) 担任关键职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/deutsche-bank-taps-ubs-s-gasser-to-run-german-wealth-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 10:09:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙坏账银行将开始出售价值 8 亿欧元的房地产部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/spain-s-bad-bank-to-start-sale-of-800-million-real-estate-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙坏账银行计划出售房地产开发商 Arqura Homes，这是其最大的持股之一，资产价值约为 8 亿欧元（8.94 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/spain-s-bad-bank-to-start-sale-of-800-million-real-estate-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 10:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰总理民调支持率上升，提前选举压力加大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/ireland-pm-s-poll-boost-adds-pressure-to-call-an-early-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《爱尔兰时报》民意调查显示，爱尔兰现任总理西蒙·哈里斯的支持率随着其政党支持率的上升而大幅上升，这一结果可能会给他在今年秋天举行大选带来更大压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/ireland-pm-s-poll-boost-adds-pressure-to-call-an-early-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 10:03:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际能源署预计俄罗斯将停止通过乌克兰输送天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/iea-says-it-s-planning-for-end-of-russian-gas-flows-via-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际能源署预计，今年年底过境协议到期后，俄罗斯天然气将停止通过乌克兰输送，并警告称，基辅及其邻国将面临严峻的冬天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/iea-says-it-s-planning-for-end-of-russian-gas-flows-via-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 09:00:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洪水使捷克 18 亿美元紧缩计划受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/czech-government-plans-to-boost-budget-deficit-due-to-floods</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克共和国计划今年和明年增加财政赤字，以应对大面积洪水造成的损失，这对政府控制国家债务的雄心又一次打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/czech-government-plans-to-boost-budget-deficit-due-to-floods</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 08:49:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲电动汽车销量暴跌促使汽车制造商寻求欧盟援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/germany-s-slump-in-ev-sales-drags-on-europe-s-auto-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国电动汽车市场上个月暴跌，导致欧洲整体电动汽车市场出现下滑，迫使汽车制造商呼吁布鲁塞尔重新考虑关键的气候目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/germany-s-slump-in-ev-sales-drags-on-europe-s-auto-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
